_json.gridTitle: Rabbitat heaven...ideas to make your rabbit's living space AMAZING! - Small Pet Select | Your #1 Source for Timothy Hay
_json.description: Is your friend’s living space the envy of all his Facebook friends?  Does your little animal have a Pinterest page showing off her digs?  There are some terrific ideas out there. Having a well-designed and furnished space is not only brag-worthy, it helps keep the little ones happier, busier, and it can even help them get more exercise.  The biggest plus: a great living area is easier to have in a central area of your home, so you and your animal interact more, and they can be a bigger part ...
